  <div class="h-full mb-4 mt-12 w-full flex flex-col justify-center container" id="onboarding">
    <style>
        #onboarding ul li:nth-child(odd) {
            margin-left: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        #onboarding ul li:nth-child(even) {
            margin-left: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-center font-bold mb-12">Onboarding Process</h1>
    <p class="font-bold">Onboarding Process for Premium Access with SigmaTenders:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc mt-4">
      <li class="">Registration and Verification:</li>
      <li class="">Sign up with your Gmail ID on our website. Verify your email by logging in and checking your inbox
        (including spam) for the verification link.
      </li>
      <li>Customization:</li>
      <li>Log in to your account and customise your tender searches by adding or removing keywords according to your
        interests.
      </li>
