      </li>
      <li>Activation and Access:</li>
      <li>Upon receipt of your payment proof and user ID, our team will activate your paid account. Enjoy full access to
        our tender portal resources, including email notifications and tender searches.
      </li>
      <li>Email Preferences:</li>
      <li>Customize the frequency of email notifications directly in your registered email ID to stay updated on your
        saved queries.
      </li>
